{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"stem·spark\n          \n            Learning\n            Connect\n            Resources\n            Join us\n          \n        \n\n        \n        \n          \n            Every woman in STEM\n            \n              changes the equation\n            \n          \n          \n            Resources, mentors, and community. We bring it all together so you can focus on what matters — your work.\n          \n          \n            Explore resources\n            How it works\n          \n        \n\n        \n        \n          \n            500+\n            curated resources\n            Courses · Scholarships · Programs\n          \n          \n            120+\n            mentors ready\n            1-on-1 · Group · Async\n          \n          \n            \"I found my first research position through STEMSpark. The mentorship directory changed everything.\"\n            — Priya, computational biology\n          \n        \n\n      \n    \n    \n      B. Warm Organic\n      Soft, sculptural, alive. Blob shapes, overlapping cards at slight angles, warm gradients. Fraunces serif gives it personality without being stuffy. Feels like a brand that a creative studio designed — not a template.\n      \n        Organic shapes\n        Overlapping cards\n        Slight rotations\n        Warm gradients\n        Fraunces serif","choice":"b","id":null,"timestamp":1774992562779}
